          </dt>
          <dd id="text" class="mb-0 ml-3 markdownify">We the People is an interactive and exciting way to bring the soul
            of the
            american constitution alive using technology. I helped to create this website as part of a team, our
            objective was to pack the contents of the constitution into a fun, digestible product for generations of
