          </dt>
          <dd id="text" class="mb-0 ml-3 markdownify">While I was living in San Francisco, I became aware of the massive
            homeless epidemic, and how difficult it was to find restrooms that were open to the public. This app was
            created as the solution to this problem and aims to increase the accessibility of public restrooms.</dd>

          <dt>
            <a href="http://politicking.herokuapp.com/" target="blank" id="text"
              style="font-variant: small-caps; ">POLITICKING</a>
          </dt>
          <dd id="text" class="mb-0 ml-3 markdownify">A common issue amongst voters is being unaware of the policy, and
            more
            important details regarding candidates. This application is perfectly positioned to solve this problem, one
            feature of this application is to offer a quiz with simple questions, and then matches that user with a
            candidate with values most aligned to them.</dd>

